Take dwc_cmd0 as an example. If you want to test a different module, simply replace the module name in the commands below.

1. Install Icarus Verilog
   Make sure Icarus Verilog is installed on your system.

2. Open a terminal in the directory containing your source files and run:
   iverilog -g2012 -o simv_dwc_cmd0 dwc_cmd0_tb.sv dwc_cmd0.sv
   vvp .\simv_dwc_cmd0 
   gtkwave dwc_cmd0_tb.vcd 
